=====================================================

### Tender Details

* **Reference Number**: PW-23-01020563
* **Solicitation Number**: T8157-220011
* **Publication Date**: January 9, 2023
* **Tender Closing Date**: January 23, 2023 (15:00:00)
* **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Selective tendering
* **Procurement Category**: SRV (Services)
* **Trade Agreements**: Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA), Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA), Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)

### Tender Overview

Transport Canada seeks to hire a TSPS Senior Business Analyst (APM - Services professionnels centrés sur les tâches et les solutions) to support the organization in its business operations.

### Contact Information

* **Point of Contact**: Cory Lajoie, cory.lajoie@tc.gc.ca, 204-228-2267
* **Address**: 344 Edmonton Street, Winnipeg, MB, R3C 0P6
